{"tid":2186403,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"呃like議員伍健偉宣佈改FB page名繼續營運 比藍屍衝入嚟圍插","createTime":"2020-09-03T02:51:08.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-03T13:00:08.000Z","uid":35324,"like":6,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"cac87c1bd5a7fd7150975ab12e2cb931a6f0ea2a","tid":2186403,"uid":35324,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-03T02:51:08.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/2354413427970468/posts/3293363280742140/?d=n\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F2354413427970468%2Fposts%2F3293363280742140%2F%3Fd%3Dn&d=DfqNtxIahorWM%2FuK5ta3hYeonPPUtn1HApnj2AcFxYA%3D&h=744e5345\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/2354413427970468/posts/3293363280742140/?d=n</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/u1uNpwa.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fu1uNpwa.png&h=da1d1ae8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n大量藍屍衝入個post留相同comment串鳩伍健偉唔quit<br />\n<br />\n但講真，我估like上面呢個comment嗰百幾人入面，應該有唔少都係黃<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 情緒勒索做臭咗個朵，最後又唔夠like...<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n不過大家唔介意嘅，都可以入去撐下佢，繼續like佢page嘅<br />\n畢竟佢而家都話肯改page名做社運野，撐下佢點都好過比藍屍笑"},{"pid":"05a52fa049a7846bbb10b88c18be1edcfc378043","tid":2186403,"uid":200529,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-03T02:53:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6a01420cc5332504206c0b31f9544a2fbf4d7b5f","tid":2186403,"uid":5490,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-03T02:55:34.000Z","msg":"佢夠like數點解要走？"},{"pid":"784e7999525b1f2dcceda8f12a423fde6dd44c90","tid":2186403,"uid":59818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-09-03T02:55:43.000Z","msg":"估唔到唔夠數<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 唔係頭一兩日已經差唔多追到咩<br />\n<br />\nBtw嗰陣林進同黃百羽講話「你憑咩認為佢真係唔會辭職」 依家奶野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2bed72e8e7d05431d9eb2b356afcc47465f95f28","tid":2186403,"uid":71092,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-03T02:56:12.000Z","msg":"無撚聊<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wfc2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"679201116f67b191be707abec745b3b4b7feb11a","tid":2186403,"uid":231583,"like":7,"dislike":1,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-03T02:58:24.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"5b534030f8d66f161de47c18115f99cbaa7276fc","tid":2186403,"uid":35324,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-03T03:00:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/FSRzO1G.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FFSRzO1G.png&h=9c76d692&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n有page話唔咁做邊有人關心<br />\n講真，之前啲post都見唔少新西人話伍健偉落手落腳做野，好勤力，讚到佢係全港最好<br />\n<br />\n真係想要like嘅，even話幫新西整個page嘅，你直接po上連登講，實大把人心甘情願嚟支持你<br />\n但而家like得你嘅，我諗有一半都係帶住唔gur嘅心情like...<br />\n班熱狗更加會大力恥笑你<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3cf967fa4d889be3993eba96ad692ad9dfac3f87","tid":2186403,"uid":1729,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"quote":{"pid":"784e7999525b1f2dcceda8f12a423fde6dd44c90","tid":2186403,"uid":59818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-09-03T02:55:43.000Z","msg":"估唔到唔夠數<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 唔係頭一兩日已經差唔多追到咩<br />\n<br />\nBtw嗰陣林進同黃百羽講話「你憑咩認為佢真係唔會辭職」 依家奶野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-03T03:00:36.000Z","msg":"幾日就夠數啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 藍屍講咩就信<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6e388bb3b18ec0fba1634aba364b8b4ad0aee058","tid":2186403,"uid":59818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3cf967fa4d889be3993eba96ad692ad9dfac3f87","tid":2186403,"uid":1729,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"quote":{"pid":"784e7999525b1f2dcceda8f12a423fde6dd44c90","tid":2186403,"uid":5